r apart, and everyone tried to grab a little. As a result, there was almost nothing to eat.\nThe harira was burnt to a crisp, and so was the Chinese soup. The food quality was really poor. The dessert was very mediocre (see\"</p><div class=\"author\">— selma el</div></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#f5d7a0\">Nous rejoindre</div>\n      <h2>Venez nous voir</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-grid\">\n      <div class=\"contact-info\">\n        <h3>Informations</h3>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">📍</span><div><strong>Adresse</strong><br>J85X+VCG Complexe au Petit Rocher, Casablanca 20160, Morocco</div></div>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">📞</span><div><strong>Téléphone</strong><br><a href=\"tel:+212522363604\">+212 5 22 36 36 04</a></div></div>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">🕐</span><div><strong>Horaires</strong><ul class='hours'><li><strong>Monday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Tuesday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Wednesday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Thursday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Friday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Saturday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li><li><strong>Sunday</strong><span>12:30 PM to 12 AM</span></li></ul></div></div>\n        <a href=\"https://wa.me/212522363604\" class=\"wa-cta\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">💬 Écrivez-nous sur WhatsApp</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"map-wrap\">\n        <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=El+Cenador%2C+J85X%2BVCG+Complexe+au+Petit+Rocher%2C+Casablanca+20160%2C+Morocco&amp;output=embed\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<footer>\n